cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper is related to speech technology and automatic speech recognition, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of neural models, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed technique for data selection is based on similarity criteria, which is related to data mining (cs.SI) and statistical learning (cs.SD).
